50:53.856 --> 51:05.614
And the whole thing, he turned her into a suitable wife of William Morris, who had grown up in this high level of high standards.

51:07.602 --> 51:19.097
Well, no sooner had they had the two daughters in the first two years of their marriage, but she takes the kids and goes to live with Rosetti.

51:19.117 --> 51:20.759
Or no, wait a minute, there's an interim.

51:21.901 --> 51:28.950
