51:40.278 --> 51:42.281
We mustn't have a scandal."

51:42.301 --> 51:43.141
It was very British.

51:43.522 --> 51:46.425
Unthinkable, exactly.

51:46.445 --> 51:51.230
So he wrote to her almost every day and became the visitor and the kids there.

51:52.691 --> 52:05.605
Well, my theory is he was so full of fury, and rather than directing the fury and throttling all of them, he

